Automatically adds newly created nodes to the specified nodequeue. (Edit getTypeMap to return an array which maps content types you want to track to nodequeue IDs.) 

Code has basically been generalised from this Stack Overflow answer: http://stackoverflow.com/a/10483181/22946

Code is not up to drupal.org standards, and I should probably knock up some sort of admin config stuff too. Use with caution.